libpod/runtime_ctr.go:804-808
```golang
	for _, ctr := range ctrs {
		include := true
		for _, filter := range filters {
			include = include && filter(ctr)
		}

		if include {
			ctrsFiltered = append(ctrsFiltered, ctr)
		}
	}
```
This code determines that if one of the filter conditions is not met, it will not match.
